title: CacheGetMetadata
name: CacheGetMetadata
description: returns a structure with some Metadata regarding the cache elements (keys returned depends on the Cache type used).

arguments.name: id
arguments.description: name of the element you need metadat for

arguments.name: cacheName
arguments.description: definition of the cache used by name, when not set the "default Object Cache" defined in Lucee Administrator is used instead.
